snippet.title: Logic - Trailer
snippet.description:
My first ever big game, Logic, is finally aviable!
Check out on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2558090/Logic/
Game's website: https://smiterik.github.io/logic/

Music used in the video: Machinimasound - Remember the Dreams (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5OqMU2wIh1Q)

Logic is a 3D logical platform game, where you can get through the levels by solving several different puzzles with the help of moveable cubes, by switching buttons and pressure plates, and by using elevators and teleporting platforms.
